<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE CORNER BAR: MORE BARS: 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By FRANK MESSINA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Heritage Brewing Co., 24921 Dana Point Harbor Drive, Dana Point. Open Sundays 
through Thursdays from 11:30 a.m. to midnight; Fridays and Saturdays till 2 
a.m. (714) 240-2060. 
</P>
<P>
Currently the only pub in Orange County that makes its own beer on the 
premises: three menu-listed ales daily plus a different specialty brew every 
couple of weeks. All are rich, flavorful and heads above many English beers. 
Plus, there's even reggae music on Sundays. FRANK MESSINA 
</P>
</TEXT>
