<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA091390-0060 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 275351 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 13, 1990, Thursday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 1 
</P>
