FORCES -- KUWAIT; UNITED NATIONS SECURITY COUNCIL; UNITED NATIONS -- IRAQ; 
UNITED NATIONS -- UNITED STATES; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; 
BLOCKADES; FOOD DISTRIBUTION; EMBARGOES; EVACUATIONS; AMERICANS -- KUWAIT; 
AMERICANS -- IRAQ; VIDEO RECORDINGS; BUSH, GEORGE; TELEVISION BROADCASTS; 
RELOCATION OF PEOPLE 
</P>
