</P>
<P>
Occupation: Owner-operator of a doughnut shop. 
</P>
<P>
Background: Six years on Planning Commission. Backing of city employee groups, 
Mayor Donna Smith and leaders of recall effort against former Councilman C. L. 
(Clay) Bryant. 
</P>
<P>
Promises: Improved council-school board relations. "You can't have a quality 
city without quality schools." 
</P>
<P>
</P>
