<P>
Photo, Rosemont pupils Tanya Campos, left, Tanya Lizano practice dance. ROBERT 
DURELL / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Betty Thomas will introduce Bread and Puppet 
Theater on Saturday. 
</P>
