12-inch 
</P>
<P>
* Information: (714) 497-0716, Ron Lutz 
</P>
<P>
LAGUNA NIGUEL (YMCA) 
</P>
<P>
* Cost: $35 non-member, $30 members; full team $360 to $420 (12 players 
required) 
</P>
<P>
* League options: men's and co-ed, slow pitch (with 12-foot pitch arc) 
</P>
<P>
* Sign-ups: Tomorrow, 5 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
* Information: (714) 831-YMCA, Derek or Eric 
</P>
<P>
